      "span_text": "Downstream of the cryostat was a steel/scintillator tail-catcher, in the same configuration as was used in a 1998 beam test  , with three thick scintillator plates of 140x140 cm 2 cross-sectional area followed by four 50x50 cm 2 counters.",
